description:
&lt;p&gt;Warwick House Medical Practice is situated in the South East corner of Taunton within easy access of junction 25 of the M5 motorway. It serves a mixed urban and semi-rural population of 7,500 patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We take pride in nurturing a friendly, informal and supportive environment in which to work whilst ensuring we deliver high quality, person -centred care to our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit a Contract Performance and Quality Co-ordinator to become an integral part of our management team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A key function of this post is to work in conjunction with the Operational Manager, to develop, implement and maintain effective procedures for managing the performance of the clinical contracts held by the practice and to support the Operational Manager in maximising practice income. This will include running regular reports and data analysis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will also be responsible for the efficient delivery of administration processes, and for liaising with the Patient Services Team Leader to ensure the efficient coordination of all inter-related administration processes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They will also deputise for the Operational Manager when required&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a unique and exciting opportunity for a motivated and highly organized individual with good people, administration, data management and communication skills to join our friendly team. Successful applicants will have excellent IT skills. A Primary Care background &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;or&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; knowledge of QOF &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;or &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;performance management experience is ideal for this post&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We welcome informal discussions about this post and would encourage you to contact us for further information.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameSian MaraJob titleOperational ManagerEmail addresssian.mara@nhs.netTelephone number01823 282147&lt;/p&gt;
